data.actual_result: It is a bit transparent when looking closely at the left side of it. You can see the server icons and the channel names for example.
data.short_description: [iPad with iOS 9.3.5 only] Keyboard is a bit transparent
data.steps_to_repro: - Make sure you are using dark theme - Go to any text chat and open the keyboard by clicking on the text field - Observe the transparency of the keyboard (on the left side)
